title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to Short - Discover The Latest Changes after an update
description:
In this short I will show you a quick way how to identity which content has been updated by looking at the timestamp on the directory level. This will help you understanding which items have been updated after you did for example install Sim Update 15 beta.
